dden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>
<p>·      Shooters will have 60 seconds to make as many-3-pointers as possible.</p>
<p>·      Men shooters will use the provided men's regulation size ball.</p>
<p>·      Women shooters will use the provided women's regulation size ball.</p>
<p>·      Only legally attempted shots, both feet behind the arc at the release of the ball, will count.</p>
<p>·      Each shooter needs to have a designated rebounder for the entirety of the shootout, or may have a member f the Rec Sports staff rebound for them.</p>
<p>·      NBA style: 5 spots with 3 balls each. You must finish each spot before moving onto the next.</p>
<p>·      The top 4 shooters from each division (men's/women') will advance to the finals.</p>
